{
  "stem": "717.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we asked the people there-- I met a few guys that were from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know them, but they told me they were from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told them who we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, that we-- they're supposed to take us to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, are you crazy?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's nobody here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What gas chambers?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you see anybody?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Do you see any Germans behind you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't take our names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he asked, are you hungry?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, of course, we're hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't eat for two days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So there were these small can, about that high, 25 liters or 20 liters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, help yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was about half full with soup, thick, frozen, already cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I put my head in with my hands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I ate.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the beginning of the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I stayed in that hospital until the 27th when we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And since I was well, I wasn't sick, we tended to the sick people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were people with broken arms, half the surgeries, open bellies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we cleaned the toilets, and we, we cooked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We served them the food, but we already had plenty of food then because we grabbed out of the, the magazines that they kept the food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few days before, they managed to send in-- I think it was two days, on the Thursday, the 25th-- a truck or two trucks came in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they called up, everybody should go down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going to take us away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With me in that-- in that hospital was a guy from the Vienna [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From the soccer team, the first 11, [INAUDIBLE], I remember his name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had his legs broken eight time when they bombed the camp that he was in.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
